snippet.title: Touchgrind BMX - Release trailer
snippet.description:
Available for iOS on Apple App Store: https://itunes.apple.com/en/app/touchgrind-bmx/id426072035?mt=8

Also available on Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=se.illusionlabs.bmx&hl=en

lllusion Labs is proud to announce the worlds first true multitouch BMX game, Touchgrind BMX.

Become a BMX pro and perform spectacular tricks in locations all over the world. The evolvement of the innovative multi-touch controls used in the original Touchgrind game together with the real physics simulation let you perform a vast amount of trick combinations - your skill and imagination are the only limits.
